ActivityMetadata.Name: ZM Subscribe to Plans
ActivityMetadata.Label: ZM Subscribe to Plans
ActivityMetadata.Description: Subscribe plans for a Sub Account under a Master Account. The plans can only be subscribed for an existing free Sub Account and the subscriptions charge for these plans should be paid by a Master Account. Zoom only assigns this privilege to trusted partners and only approved partners can use this API. Contact the [**ISV team**](https://zoom.us/plan/api) for more details. **Scopes**: `billing:master`
